AVI_Reader - Class in function.movieTools
ImageJ Plugin for reading an AVI file into an image stack (one slice per video frame) Restrictions and Notes: - Only few formats supported: - uncompressed 8 bit with palette (=LUT) - uncompressed 8 & 16 bit grayscale - uncompressed 24 & 32 bit RGB (alpha channel ignored) - uncompressed 32 bit AYUV (alpha channel ignored) - various YUV 4:2:2 compressed formats - png or jpeg-encoded individual frames.
